'''Alili''' (Assaɣ amassnan Nerium oleander) iga yan wanaw n [[Asklu|tddagin]], d llan kigan n wanawn yaḍni ɣ yat tawja macc alili a bahra i ttussann. Iga ammɣay i mmu iggut ustci d iga anakram (anakram: immɣayn iɣ illa ustci) ar ittili kigan ɣ igʷmmaḍ n isaffn, d ar ittili ɣ tmizar yuggan ill umlil amjahdi ar [[Ccinwa]].

== Asnuml n tddagt ==
Iga wlili yat taddagt mẓẓin tamazrayt ar tlkkm tiɣzi ns gr 2 d 6 n id mitru, d ar itteṭṭaf kigan n igjja. Ifrawn n taddagt ad gan uqmirn ṭṭafn ixf imsadn, ar ttisdidn ɣ uzddar, tzur, udm ns n uflla izgzaw kigan d udm n uzddar tazgzut ns tdrus.

D tzgzaw bdda taddagt.

== Ajjig ==
Ijjign n ulili gan imjahdin s uklu umlil nɣ-d azwiwɣ nɣ-d amagẓay, d illa gisn ustci kigan.

== Tamawalt ==

* Ill umlil amjahdi = البحر الأبيض
* Tamazrayt = معمرة
* Uqmirn = ضيقون
* Amagẓay = ارجواني

